featured_reviews.review_id: Easy to approach Masjid / Mosque for offering prayers (Namaz / Salah) in Jangpura, New Delhi. While coming from Nizamuddin side, it is on left hand side of Jangpura signal, whereas while approaching from Ashram side it is on right hand side at the same traffic signal (after Bhogal on Mathura Rd.). One need to walk almost 25 meters side by side of DDA park to reach the Masjid / Mosque. There is empty space for parking vehicles too. The mosque is small but has 3 floors and basement to accommodate worshippers. Friday / Jumua prayer time is 1:15 p.m. / 13:15 hours.
